# MDC Syntax Showcase

This document demonstrates the **expressive power** of _Markdown Components (MDC)_ syntax, combining traditional markdown with Vue-like components. You can read more about MDC at [Nuxt Content Documentation](https://content.nuxt.com/usage/markdown).

## Inline Formatting Examples

Here's some **bold text**, _italic text_, **_bold and italic_**, and `inline code`. You can also use ~~strikethrough~~ text and create [links to external sites](https://example.com) or reference `variables` in your content.

Use `code` for technical terms like `useState()` or `const theme = 'dark'` within sentences.

