## Code Blocks with Highlighting

```javascript
// Syntax highlighting example
function generateTheme(colors, mood) {
  const { primary, secondary, accent } = colors;
  return {
    background: mood === 'dark' ? '#1a1a1a' : '#ffffff',
    foreground: primary,
    accent: accent || secondary
  };
}
```

